Reports a reference to a variable, mixin, or function that is declared in another file but this file isn't 
explicitly <a href="https://sass-lang.com/documentation/at-rules/import">imported</a> in the current file.
<p><b>Example:</b></p>
<pre><code>
* {
  margin: $var-in-other-file;
}
</code></pre>
<!-- tooltip end -->
